11 Sec. 2. RULEMAKING
12 The Public Utility Commission shall update its Rule 5.100 to allow ground
13 mounted photovoltaic net metering systems of 25 kilowatts and less to qualify
14 for expedited registration. It is the intent of the General Assembly that the
15 Commission shall allow systems of 25 kilowatts and less to use the expedited
16 registration before the rules are updated.
